Most of the images of Russia’s attacks on our nation are deleted from social media, blocked, or censored as “shocking content”. Yes, it is most definitely shocking, and we are fully aware of how shocking they are as they reflect the daily life of any Ukrainian. I’m not going to share the most horrific photos with you today, but I want to share those that touched my life so much so that a day doesn’t go by that I don’t think of them. I want to share them with you so you would have a chance to clearly see that we are in a fight for our lives with absolute evil. And they aren’t just trying to destroy us, they will bring famine and death anywhere they can just to lift sanctions. <img data-lazy-fallback="1" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1335074" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456282121.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="898" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456282121.jpg 932w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456282121.jpg?resize=385,480 385w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456282121.jpg?resize=768,958 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456282121.jpg?resize=720,898 720w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456282121.jpg?resize=350,437 350w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px"  /> <img data-lazy-fallback="1" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1335075" src="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456288313.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="900" srcset="https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456288313.jpg 1080w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456288313.jpg?resize=384,480 384w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/FB_IMG_1657456288313.jpg?resize=768,960 768w, https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/wp-content/up